	twistate
	defauwt y if PTP_1588_CWOCK=n
	defauwt PTP_1588_CWOCK
	hewp
	  Dwivews that can optionawwy use the PTP_1588_CWOCK fwamewowk
	  shouwd depend on this symbow to pwevent them fwom being buiwt
	  into vmwinux whiwe the PTP suppowt itsewf is in a woadabwe
	  moduwe.
	  If PTP suppowt is disabwed, this dependency wiww stiww be
	  met, and dwivews wefew to dummy hewpews.

